## Step 6 — Create a ReferenceGrant (if app namespace differs from Gateway namespace)

Since the app lives in `web` and the Gateway lives in `nginx-gateway`, an HTTPRoute needs explicit permission to reference the Service cross-namespace:

```yaml
# referencegrant.yaml
apiVersion: gateway.networking.k8s.io/v1beta1
kind: ReferenceGrant
metadata:
  name: allow-gateway-to-web
  namespace: web
spec:
  from:
  - group: gateway.networking.k8s.io
    kind: HTTPRoute
    namespace: web
  to:
  - group: ""
    kind: Service
    name: web-app-svc
```

```bash
kubectl apply -f referencegrant.yaml
```

